# Xcode
#
# Based on GitHub's Swift/Xcode template, extended with North Finance safeguards.

## User settings
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate

## Obj-C/Swift specific
*.hmap

## Build output
DerivedData/
build/
*.xcresult

## App packaging and signing
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM
*.mobileprovision
*.p12
*.cer

## Playgrounds
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/
Packages/

## CocoaPods
# Pods are intentionally not ignored. The project does not currently use
# CocoaPods; define the repository policy before adding it.

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

